						Code Jam

email id : <jithusunnyk.gmail.com>

Design:

	step 1: Collect all the trigrams from the story and save it in a list(trigram_list)
	step 2: Using a function Trigram_Match() find the matching trigrams and form the story with number of words not greater than 300
	step 3: Select any random trigram as the title of the story and print it
	
	
Dependencies :

		Use standard python library's.(python2.5)
		Platform : Ubuntu Linux

Usage :
	
	python 	ngram.py
	
	The story used for generating the story should be stored on the same directory.
